We don't have In-N-Out in Oregon so every time I'm in CA I go. I was thrilled to find they had one near our hotel and would've eaten it for every meal if I could but self-control kicked in. This place was speedy considering the lunch rush, the staff friendly and the food AMAZING! I can't believe how inexpensive it is and appreciate the quality coming out of a fast food joint which I normally avoid. Still drooling thinking of my burger...

