Okay so I worked at Starbucks for 7 years so I know how it should go and this one was not good. It's DT only which sucks as I was from out of town and wanted a second to see all they had (selection varies from market to market). We drove through and speed was okay but my drink was not. My shots were clearly bad and the milk wasn't steamed correctly. I brought it back to be re-made and they didn't really apologize or acknowledge the problem. At the time I was a partner so I was really surprised. I'd try Coffee Bean over this place any day.

